<template>
  <v-container>
    <v-card
     outlined
     >
        <v-card-title>CONFIRMAR ENTREGA #{{$route.params.number}} ?</v-card-title>
        <v-card-actions>
            <v-btn 
                v-on:click = 'goToMap()'
                dark
                color="indigo"
            > SAIR PARA A ENTREGA
            </v-btn>
        </v-card-actions>
    </v-card>
  </v-container>
</template>

<script>
    export default {
        name: 'entregaCard',
        data(){
            return {
                msg: 'card',
                show: false
            }
        },
        props: [
          'numero_da_entrega',
        ],
        methods: {
            goToMap : function(){
                this.$router.push({ path: '/mapa'})
            }
        }
    }
</script>
